lyrics:
говноед безумный надо мной живёт
он не затыкаясь целый день орёт
что-бы спать спокойно и нормально жить
гниду бесноватую на кол посадить.

[Verse 1]
Dancing in the neon lights, we're feeling high tonight
Pop music taking over, it's a sound that feels so right
Melodies that make us move, from dusk until the dawn
We're lost within the rhythm, can't resist its sweet con

[Chorus]
Pop, pop, it's the beat we can't deny
Hands up in the air, we're reaching for the sky
Let the music guide us, we won't stop the flow
Together we are one, in this pop-filled show
